{"tid":765045,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓戰遺骸運抵美國　特朗普:感謝金正恩信守諾言","createTime":"2018-08-02T12:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T23:15:35.000Z","uid":62257,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa639c1b09064a2bc6e4354b486f445c7d5d5f1","tid":765045,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:36:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180802/mobile/bknint-20180802093034229-0802_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180802%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20180802093034229-0802_17011_001.html&d=0%2Fn9LnBUZpXCn3HzwSPaeuPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=95568afa\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180802/mobile/bknint-20180802093034229-0802_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n北韓早前向美國歸還的55具疑為韓戰陣亡美軍遺骸，於當地時間周三（1日）運抵夏威夷作進一步分析及辨認身份。美國總統特朗普其後在社交網發文，感謝北韓領袖金正恩遵守承諾，又稱期待不久後與他見面。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每副放有遺骸的棺木都以美國國旗覆蓋，並在一名海軍陸戰隊隊員、一名海軍、一名陸軍士兵及一名空軍人員陪同下，依次放在夏威夷一個基地的機庫內。在轉移棺木的過程期間，副總統彭斯把右手放在左胸前，同場的美國印度洋－太平洋司令部司令戴維森亦敬禮。部分獲邀出席儀式的韓戰失蹤美軍家屬，見到棺木時哭起來。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n彭斯表示，歸還遺骸一事讓韓戰失蹤美軍家屬帶來新希望。特朗普則在貼文感謝金正恩，開始歸還韓戰美軍遺骸，直言對他的善舉並不感到驚訝。他寫道：「同時，感謝你的友好信件，我期待不久後與你見面。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據美方資料，總共有7700名美軍在韓戰期間失蹤，當中估計約5300人的遺骸在北韓境內。其中一名失蹤美軍家屬表示，得悉北韓歸還遺骸的新聞時，希望其中一具遺骸便是他們的親人。美國國防部官員透露，可能要花上至少數個月、甚至長達數年的時間，才能驗證這批遺骸的身份。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"14ea6c842eae927ae726830a9eaa0224bdb19f4e","tid":765045,"uid":62257,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/203754_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F203754_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e3019335&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7e76ac6747214a3003fc589edfe8e545d1c773e","tid":765045,"uid":17008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"特朗普則在貼文感謝金正恩，開始歸還韓戰美軍遺骸<br />\n<br />\n開始？還曬啦會唔會？"},{"pid":"37a48a399204c51acb15b802534df8b48cde8d87","tid":765045,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:41:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acd5ba8da95f335bf18f226cb42e01bdb1582207","tid":765045,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"好似未驗好哂係咪全部&quot;真骨&quot;WO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一陣又俾金金玩偷龍轉鳳點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4401995a2e905c1876f6f9fbd502f3190fdaf504","tid":765045,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:41:21.000Z","msg":"奧巴馬uccu"},{"pid":"4667ecad0a9d0a05160fe46919634c867409989e","tid":765045,"uid":17008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37a48a399204c51acb15b802534df8b48cde8d87","tid":765045,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:41:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:48:47.000Z","msg":"你又知入面唔係碎？"},{"pid":"1be078888afed6f82118933fcdceedc8b0bbe351","tid":765045,"uid":104026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:51:48.000Z","msg":"金仔 : 求其執幾副骨俾佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86dd946d5b7b942f25e53057a4e931a987e8e039","tid":765045,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T23:15:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}